messages.message: Hi All, last week our production environment was quite unstable.  We did a deep dive on all the issues that we saw, what we did to resolve them in short / medium term, and what are we planning to do in the long term to fix the issues.  Please take a look at the document and add your comments / suggestions: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1SfSr7CD1JQ9lnDkX6HXNwuMxmzDXPMha9mf_lgVhfKI/edit
